===========================================================================
                              依赖关系
===========================================================================

bo/ (业务对象模块):
  - ai_worker.py: 依赖 task.py
  - task.py: 无外部依赖
  - task_flow_group.py: 依赖 task.py
  - tasks_graph.py: 依赖 task.py, task_flow_group.py (延迟导入)
  - task_manifest.py: 依赖 task_flow_group.py
  - role.py: 无外部依赖
  - organization.py: 依赖 ai_worker.py, task.py

simulation_process_module.py:
  - 依赖: bo/task_manifest.py (TaskManifest)
  - 依赖: bo/organization.py (Organization)
  - 依赖: simulation_process_engine.py (SimulationProcessEngine)
  - 依赖: task_dispatch_engine.py (TaskDispatchEngine)

task_dispatch_engine.py:
  - 依赖: bo/task_manifest.py (TaskManifest)
  - 依赖: bo/task_flow_group.py (TaskFlowGroup)
  - 依赖: bo/task.py (StartTask, EndTask)
  - 依赖: simulation_process_engine.py (SimulationProcessEngine)

simulation_process_engine.py:
  - 依赖: bo/organization.py (Organization, OrganizationFactory)
  - 依赖: bo/ai_worker.py (AIWorker)
  - 依赖: bo/task.py (Task, StartTask)
  - 依赖: worker_type_registry.py (WorkerTypeRegistry)

worker_type_registry.py:
  - 依赖: bo/ai_worker.py (AIWorker)

generate_graph_and_flows.py:
  - 依赖: bo/tasks_graph.py (TasksGraph)
  - 依赖: bo/task_flow_group.py (TaskFlowGroup)

